---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Research — Brendan Bennett">
  <h1>Research</h1>
  <p class="intro">A selection of ongoing and past research interests.</p>

  <article class="entry">
    <h2>Computational Approaches to Complex Systems</h2>
    <p>
      Exploring how computational models can help us understand emergent
      behaviour in large-scale systems. This work combines simulation,
      statistical analysis, and theoretical frameworks to uncover patterns
      that aren't visible at smaller scales.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="entry">
    <h2>Data-Driven Methods in the Sciences</h2>
    <p>
      Investigating the application of modern data analysis techniques to
      scientific problems. Interested in how we can extract meaningful
      signal from noisy, high-dimensional datasets while maintaining
      rigorous standards of evidence.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="entry">
    <h2>Open Problems &amp; Future Directions</h2>
    <p>
      Always looking for new questions worth asking. Current interests
      include the intersection of machine learning with traditional
      scientific methodology, reproducibility in computational research,
      and tools for collaborative knowledge work.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .intro {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .entry {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .entry:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .entry h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
